dc_title_s: Insurance maps of Minneapolis, Minnesota, 1912, Volume 6
dc_description_s: Partially hand-colored. Each volume includes a map of ward lines and district lines and a volume boundary map. Volume 6 includes Big Island Park, Browndale Mills, Crystal Bay, Excelsior, Hopkins, Long Lake, Minnetonka Beach, Minnetonka Mills, Mound, Spring Park, St. Louis Park, Tonka Bay, Wayzata, Richfield and specials in Richfield Township and on shores of Lake Minnetonka.|v.6: sheets 601-713|70 Centimeters|Scale 1:600. 50 feet to 1 inch|City of Minneapolis Archives
